/-- `‚Ñù‚â•0‚àû` is `MeasurableEquiv` to `‚Ñù‚â•0 ‚äï Unit`. -/
def ennrealEquivSum : ‚Ñù‚â•0‚àû ‚âÉ·µê ‚Ñù‚â•0 ‚äï Unit :=
  { Equiv.optionEquivSumPUnit ‚Ñù‚â•0 with
    measurable_toFun := measurable_of_measurable_nnreal measurable_inl
    measurable_invFun :=
